default3.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAs outlined above, the new style of forum allows the Chief Constable and relevant 
defaultsenior 
defaultofficers and staff to be questioned in detail on issues of significant public interest. Topics we have looked at so far include fraud, police standards and domestic violence and those giving evidence have been questioned not just by me and my deputy, but a by a range of pane
defaultl
defaultlists from different walks of life and political persuasions.
default&#xa0;
default3.2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAs another
default example, I recently extended the Chief Constable’s contract for three years and at one of these public forums 
defaultI asked him to outline
default his vision for GMP in the coming years. He was then questioned by a panel that included journalists, community representatives 
defaultand the leader of Rochdale Council, who also chairs the Police and Crime Steering Group (see below)
