default3.3.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultFor performance measurement, in addition to the new-style performance reports which look at GMP as a whole, I recently published similar reports for each of the districts of Greater Manchester. 
defaultThis gives residents the chance to see how police are performing in their own district, in addition to at a Greater Manchester level.
