default4.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn Greater Manchester the Police and Crime Panel comprises the nine local authority leaders, Salford City Mayor and two independent members. The seniority of the membership demonstrates how Greater Manchester local authorities value the Commissioner’s role, and demonstrates their commitment to the community safety agenda.
default&#xa0;
default4.2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultUnderpinning the P
defaultanel is a separate 
defaultSteering G
defaultroup which works with my office, po
defaultlice and partner agencies. The Steering G
defaultroup conducts specific pieces of joint work
default with police, my office and other agencies. F
defaultor example
default, the G
defaultroup has secured agreement between police and the 10 local authorities on charging for events on the highway. Shortly it will be working on a shared approach to dealing with domestic violence
default. This allows the P
defaultanel to concentrate on setting a strategic
default direction for local authority Crime and Disorder P
defaultartnerships, and focus on scrutinising my work.
default&#xa0;
default4.3.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI believe the model adopted here in Greater Manchester is the right one. The seni
defaultority of the membership of the P
defaultanel allows it to be a truly strategic group, which can also 
defaultscrutinise
default my work with authority. Having a d
defaultelivery group underpinning the P
defaultanel’s strategic overview creates opportunities for further joint working, and – as has been seen here in Greater Manchester – allows for a consensus to be built on issues where agreement has
default previously
default been challenging. 
default&#xa0;
default4.4.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI believe the role of Police and Crime Panels should be reviewed and enhanced. The ultimate sanction against any Commissioner is, of course, the ballot box and it is entirely appropriate that the final say should be the public’s. But there should be further checks and 
defaultbalances in the system to hold C
defaultommissioners to account who are not performing or who have strayed vastly from their manifesto. 
default&#xa0;
default4.5.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThis 
defaultcannot
default be used as a way of settling political grudges or playing party politics. A sensible option would be to have a recall function. But this would need to be underpinned by a 
defaultreal, and not synthetic, 
defaultpublic appetite, perhaps being activated by public petition
default with a clear minimum threshold
default, and must not undermine the democr
defaultatic legitimacy of the elected C
defaultommissioner.  
