default5.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI have worked closely with GMP to ensure a smooth transfer of staff. 
defaultI 
defaulthave agreed with GMP that all staff will transfer to 
defaultthe Chief Constable from April.
default&#xa0;
default6.0.default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe role of Cdefaultommissionerdefaults in budget and precept settingdefault&#xa0;
default6.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAs outlined above, 
defaultthere are significant pressures on police budgets. Greater Manchester Police has
default lost more than 1,000 officers . By 2016 that will have risen to nearly 2,000. By 2017, more than £137m will have been cut from GMP’s budget. 
default&#xa0;
default6.2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn this challenging climate we have to prioritise and that is why I have focused this year’s precept increase on bolstering neighbourhood policing. This model of policing is a real success story, and both the Chief Constable and I are determined to do all we can to ensure it continues. We cannot return to an era of blue light police response. Neighbourhood policing teams are part of the fabric of communities across Greater Manchester, driving up confidence and helping to keep crime down. By asking for a small additional contribution from the public, we have been able to help secure the neighbourhood policing model.  
default&#xa0;
default6.3.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultWithin the budget I have also sought where possible to encourage partnership working and funding innovative schemes to reduce demand on police and improve services to victims. So GMP and the NHS are currently running a pilot scheme where there will be immediate and better sharing of information and expertise when police are called to an incident involving an individual with mental health problems. This has been funded from money I have set aside to target mental health and the drain it puts on police resources. As this kind of scheme b
defaultears fruit, I am
default confident we can pool more resources with other agencies to try and improve services in a context of shrinking resources.
default&#xa0;
default6.4.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultSimilarly, I have worked with Victim Support and the NHS to develop a groundbreaking initiative to help get targeted support to victims of domestic violence quickly and at a much earlier point. Domestic abuse specialists will be based in Accident and Emergency units to help NHS staff identify victims domestic violence when they present at hospital and get those victims quickly and appropriately referred to support services.
default&#xa0;
default7.0.default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe effectiveness of Cdefaultommissioners in promoting local policing prioritiesdefault&#xa0;
default7.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultMy role 
defaultcannot
default be one where I sit in an of
defaultfice all day long. I have
default been elected by the people of Greater Manchester and it is really important that I 
defaultregularly 
defaultmeet as many members of the public 
defaultas possible.
default So I ensure that 
defaultI regularly visit 
defaultHomeWatch
default groups, victims’ groups, major events, formal public meetings, community projects and other events that allow me to meet the public, listen to their concerns and ideas and respond to them.
default&#xa0;
default7.2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn addition, I have a strong presence on social and new media platforms, regularly participating in 
defaultwebchats
default and responding to questions that have been raised online.
default&#xa0;
default7.3.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI also generate s
defaultignificant media coverage and engagement with local media
default with regular columns in the main papers, and appearances on media outlets. We have also worked in partnerships with the media to get messages out on major issues. For example, in November I ran an awareness month for domestic abuse to get the message out to the public that help is out there for victims and their families.
default This was aimed at combating low levels of reporting domestic violence, demonstrating clearly that police and other agencies will take domestic violence seriously, thereby building confidence for those experiencing it, and demonstrating that we all have a part to play in changing the climate of acceptance that still exists within society generally.
default&#xa0;
default8.0.default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultProgress on establishing colladefaultboration agreements with other Cdefaultommissioners, policing organisations and partnersdefault&#xa0;
default8.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI work closely, and have a good
default relationship, with all of the C
defaultommissioners in the North West, meeting regularly and looking for opportunities to work together. For larger forces, collaboration benefits can be more effectively leveraged by 
defaultworking with other agencies within 
defaultour area, rather than formal agreements with other forces. So, for example, we are developing collaboration agreements on things like design and print services and fleet management with Manchester City Council. There are significant opportunities available to work more closely with local authorities on a range of issues from human resources to finance which I am seeking to develop in the coming year. 
default&#xa0;
default8.2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultHowever
default, effective collaboration does not
default necessitate formal agreements. Informal arrangements can be just as powerful. For example, we have seen the benefits of co-locating council, police and other services in the same building, creating a new way of working that not only drives modest financial savings, but actually helps in the delivery of a better service. I am also developing a local victims’ charter with the rest of the criminal justice system partner agencies in Greater Manchester which will sit alongside the national code, but will be more user-friendly and accessible.   
default&#xa0;
