default9.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIt should go without saying that any elected representative should be committed to transparency – I am here to represent the people of Greater Manchester and they must be able to see that I am representing them well. All of the information that I am required to publish is on my website and is easily accessible through a simple search function.
